<p>The 34-year-old SAG Award winner made sure to protect herself and others from the coronavirus by wearing a surgical mask, which New York Governor Andrew Cuomo made mandatory for public outings way back on April 15.</p>

<p>As of Thursday, there have been over 240K confirmed COVID-19 cases in New York City leading to 23,708 deaths - according to Johns Hopkins University. </p>

